 other purposes,” approved "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1916-08-11"},"text":"Aug. 11, 1916","children":[],"tail":". Part A of act of "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1916-08-11"},"text":"Aug. 11, 1916","children":[],"tail":", containing the “United States Cotton Futures Act,” was repealed by section 4 of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1939-02-10/ch2"},"text":"act Feb. 10, 1939, ch. 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/53/1"},"text":"53 Stat. 1","children":[],"tail":". Part C of that act contained the “United States Warehouse Act,” and is incorporated, as amended, as section 241 et seq. of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section is comprised of part of section 1 of part B of act ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1916-08-11"},"text":"Aug. 11, 1916","children":[],"tail":". Other provisions contained in section 1 were classified to former sections 72 and 73 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idede50a46-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"1968—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/90/487"},"text":"Pub. L. 90–487","children":[],"tail":" substituted “may be cited as” for “shall be known by the short title of”."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"idede50a47-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"effectiveDateOfAmendment","id":"idede50a48-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Effective Date of 1968 Amendment","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":